To deploy to Heroku:

# Create the App
$ heroku create <app_name>

# Add the environment variables
heroku config:add --app <app_name> ISS_DB_URL=mysql://aasheit:sustainaashe@aasheheroku.csl4c2c6dzyx.us-east-1.rds.amazonaws.com/iss
...
...

# Push the code to heroku
$ hg bookmark -r <branch_name> master	# heroku has to use the master branch for deployment
$ hg push git+ssh://git@heroku.com:<app_name>.git	# requires hg-git